{
  "id": "RAW_2f9d5ff4",
  "title": "真的猜不到，2026 年 CES，最大的赢家是它",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MTMwNDMwODQ0MQ==&mid=2653096817&idx=1&sn=b5e3411266c1732343438a7a0491a8e0",
  "date": "2026-01-08 12:36:00",
  "author": "极客公园",
  "siteName": "极客公园",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p>\n   <br>\n  </p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"ignored\">\n   <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"ignored\" data-pm-slice=\"3 5 []\">\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;clear:both;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;margin-bottom:0em;margin-right:8px;text-align:center;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;vertical-align:bottom;width:100%;font-size:14px;text-align:left;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/8cu01Kavc5baH4tGiaub6Npb9iaA2ArVhicBveGEuEsZdohvtSQdCJU0hd1m8Z3IMu2iao04zTtKRt3Ut0veXUibticg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"562\" data-cropsely2=\"341\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"422\" data-imgfileid=\"505613119\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4efd7250&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F8cu01Kavc5baH4tGiaub6Npb9iaA2ArVhicBveGEuEsZdohvtSQdCJU0hd1m8Z3IMu2iao04zTtKRt3Ut0veXUibticg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:25px 18px 18px;margin:-0.6em 8px 2em;background-size:100%;letter-spacing:0.3px;clear:both;font-size:15px;min-height:1em;line-height:1.8em;background-position:100% 100%;background-color:rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;background-repeat:no-repeat;text-align:justify;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mk54rtil1abn\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span leaf=\"\">The Show must go on！</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:1px;clear:both;font-size:17px;margin-top:25px;min-height:1em;line-height:1.5em;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"text-indent:0em;font-size:16px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk54rtil18ew\"><span leaf=\"\">作者｜靖宇</span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:48px 8px 25px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mk54rtilcrm\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">在经典黑帮电影《教父 2》中，柯里昂家族的新当家、阿尔·帕西诺饰演的麦克·柯里昂，将整个家族从纽约搬到了内华达州的太浩湖，并开始将经营范围扩大到博彩行业。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mk54rtil1hff\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">1958 年，正值拉斯维加斯发展的黄金时期，著名的胡佛水坝竣工，二战后的大量劳动力和游客，蜂拥来到内华达，而拉斯维加斯这个沙漠小镇，一举成为全球知名的博彩中心。电影讲述的，正是拉斯维加斯经济起飞的时刻。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mk54rtilzeb\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">70 年前的枪火、和雪茄烟头上的红光，现在已经挪到了市中心那个被称为「大球」（Sphere）的 360° LED 屏幕上。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mk54rtil1098\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">2026 年 1 月的第二周，全球科技从业者来到「罪恶之城」（Sin City），赴一场每年的全球消费电子展 CES 之约。从科技巨头英伟达、AMD、联想，再到几个人的小团队，所有人头上顶着「AI」的光环，在这里给世界线上年初的第一次「科技大秀」。</span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"title\">\n   <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mk54njce1gji\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n     <div style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:16px;margin-right:8px;text-align:justify;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n      <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n       <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;min-width: 10%;height: auto;flex: 0 0 auto;align-self: flex-start;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n        <div style=\"isolation: isolate;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n         <div style=\"font-size: 36px;line-height: 1;letter-spacing: 0px;color: rgb(45, 113, 214);\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n          <p style=\"clear: both;min-height: 1em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk54rtil1s02\"><em><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\">01</span></strong></em></span></p>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <p mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:17px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" mpa-font-style=\"mk54rtil1glq\"><span style=\"\" mpa-is-content=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-mpa-template&quot;:&quot;t&quot;,&quot;mpa-paragraph-type&quot;:&quot;title&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;mpa-from-tpl&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;strong&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.578px; text-align: center;&quot;,&quot;mpa-from-tpl&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;mpa-is-content&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">早已「融化」的 AI</span></span></strong></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mk54rtilnnz\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">「两年前，每个展台上都印着 Gen AI 的字样，但今年要是还这么干，就显得有点落伍了。」</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mk54rtilen1\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">在极客公园「今夜科技谈」的直播中，同在拉斯维加斯参展的创业者如此评价到。2023 年由 ChatGPT 引起的大模型浪潮，早已让 AI 成为默认选项，这个时候再特地强调，意义确实不大。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mk54rtil1mqg\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">AI，早已经从展板上的大写字体，融化到展会上的每件展品之中。除了常见的 AI 眼镜、App 和机器人，冰箱再到电视、汽车，都已经成为人工智能技术的新落脚点。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mk54rtil22me\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">拉斯维加斯会展中心的中心展厅，来自全球的科技巨头，在这里布下巨大展台，展示公司最新的 Demo。更大的公司、AI 基建行业巨头，<a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MTMwNDMwODQ0MQ==&amp;mid=2653096446&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=0f6ccbca391301f89906bf06888dfef0&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"例如英伟达、AMD 和联想，则选择提前一天，公布自家公司的最新消息和产品——他们支撑着全球经济在 AI 上的期待。\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">例如英伟达、AMD 和联想，则选择提前一天，公布自家公司的最新消息和产品——他们支撑着全球经济在 AI 上的期待。</a></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mk54rtil1xp\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">在西区展厅，出行领域的巨头也是投入最大的参展商。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mk54rtiligr\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">今年，国内的吉利、长城再次参展 CES，和谷歌的 Waymo、亚马逊等巨头同台，气势不遑多让。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"image\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-w=\"4096\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"434\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=502482de&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F8cu01Kavc5baH4tGiaub6Npb9iaA2ArVhicLZt6VFngoE3oYcHVj6XT5Nh0gde5NHLbvuZiaXHUrk8Lgx8qeXpMicRA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"secondTitle\">\n   <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1em;text-align:justify;margin-right:8px;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\" data-pm-slice=\"3 2 []\"><strong style=\"text-align: left;color: rgb(255, 47, 0);font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" mpa-font-style=\"mk54rtilxn\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-weight: normal;\">吉利展台上的极氪 9X｜图片来源：极客公园</span></span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mk54rtil119g\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">在国内汽车的展台上，外国友人最常见的形容词是「Crazy」（疯狂）。国内消费者早已熟悉的彩电冰箱大沙发，每次都还能让老外惊叹不已。例如，在吉利集团的展台上，参观者围着极氪 9X、吉利银河 M9 等全尺寸 SUV，都想坐到里面看看来自东方的智能汽车魔法，或者趴地上拍「杭州湾库里南」的闪耀轮毂。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mk54rtil1mz5\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">开展前一天，<a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MTMwNDMwODQ0MQ==&amp;mid=2653096469&amp;idx=2&amp;sn=4ce5fecef262602e6c816b17711c8445&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"吉利集团曝光了全域 AI 2.0 战略和最新的高阶智驾 G-ASD 技术\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">吉利集团曝光了全域 AI 2.0 战略和最新的高阶智驾 G-ASD 技术</a>，在外国友商依然为智能化苦恼时，中国车企的 AI 早已经是「Next level」。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"image\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-w=\"4096\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"434\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f0cd079a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F8cu01Kavc5baH4tGiaub6Npb9iaA2ArVhicclVP7G9DXqgWtjIaiakVUYoF6eRWiaJcWxBibkShHZX7b9gQuvzHszX3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"secondTitle\">\n   <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1em;text-align:justify;margin-right:8px;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\" data-pm-slice=\"3 2 []\"><strong style=\"text-align: left;color: rgb(255, 47, 0);font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" mpa-font-style=\"mk54rtil1bcu\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-weight: normal;\">长城汽车 CTO 吴会肖在 CES 上曝光长城 ASL 技术和 VLA 加持的魏牌蓝山｜图片来源：极客公园</span></span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mk54rtil1yjm\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">长城的展台上，除了曝光将使用 VLA 技术的新魏牌蓝山和高山 G9 和坦克 500，还带来了灵魂摩托 S2000CL。在「巡航摩托」哈雷·戴维森的发源地，献上一款更智能、马力更强的产品，除了「致敬」，更是向美利坚消费者提供了另一种选择和可能性。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mk54rtil4s6\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">当智能化路线逐渐清晰的当下，吉利和长城这样的经典车企，追赶的速度比人们想象的更快。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mk54rtil1v3n\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">在更细小的层面上，AI 在产品上落地的速度和变化令人眼花缭乱。在南区展厅和威尼斯人酒店，更多小型创业者带来的产品，往往比大公司的产品更有意思。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mk54rtil7hw\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">例如，Cubyfan 的 Cabo AI 伙伴，是一个智能「读卡机」。和当下遍地雷同的 AI 学习机相左，Cabo 使用的是真正的纸质「卡牌」，插进塑料的机器后，孩子就可以和卡片上的 AI 角色，进行对话。Cabo 做的更像是将 AI 角色实体化，或者将传统卡牌 AI 化了，而能抓在手里的卡牌，质感要比散发悠悠蓝光的 LED 屏幕更丰富，当然也更健康。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mk54rtil50c\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">正因为 AI 进展的速度和广度，让创业者的产品，有了更宽的频谱，来释放想象力。</span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"title\">\n   <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mk54o99b12q8\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n     <div style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:16px;margin-right:8px;text-align:justify;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n      <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n       <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;min-width: 10%;height: auto;flex: 0 0 auto;align-self: flex-start;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n        <div style=\"isolation: isolate;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n         <div style=\"font-size: 36px;line-height: 1;letter-spacing: 0px;color: rgb(45, 113, 214);\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n          <p style=\"clear: both;min-height: 1em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk54rtil1h6p\"><em><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\">02</span></strong></em></span></p>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <p mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:17px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" mpa-font-style=\"mk54rtil1nyd\"><span style=\"\" mpa-is-content=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-mpa-template&quot;:&quot;t&quot;,&quot;mpa-paragraph-type&quot;:&quot;title&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;mpa-from-tpl&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;strong&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.578px; text-align: center;&quot;,&quot;mpa-from-tpl&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;mpa-is-content&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">机器人「溢出」</span></span></strong></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mk54rtilbdg\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">机器人、或者具身智能，已经是 CES 这类科技展上的「显学」，但凡一个稍微上点规模的展会上，没租两台人形机器人吸引眼球，才是怪事。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mk54rtilywx\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">本来以为 CES 上的观众们，应该早已经对满地乱跑的机器人免疫了，但没想到「铁甲钢拳」的魅力依然无人幸免。在宇树机器人的展区，中国观众已经熟知的机器人擂台赛，每次开打依然被观众里三层外三层的围住。宇树还时不时把机器人放出去「巡展」，和其他展商联动，营销这一块把老外拿捏的死死的。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"image\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-w=\"4096\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"434\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0d01a644&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F8cu01Kavc5baH4tGiaub6Npb9iaA2ArVhicf8ugH1k98EfzxqtJpVMJn1VPAfRSVKRmkJkzTf4psNqyaUn3WRTBQw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"secondTitle\">\n   <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1em;text-align:justify;margin-right:8px;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\" data-pm-slice=\"3 2 []\"><strong style=\"text-align: left;color: rgb(255, 47, 0);font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" mpa-font-style=\"mk54rtilwtt\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-weight: normal;\">机器手也是这次展会上的热点｜图片来源：极客公园</span></span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mk54rtil14fd\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">人形机器人依然是热点，但在 CES 的展馆中，机器收或者「灵巧手」这个机器人身上的部件，大有喧宾夺主的感觉。展厅中随处可见尺寸犹如「如来神掌」一般的巨型大手雕塑，吸引观众到来，看着展台上的机器手转苹果、操作流水线货物或者就是简单的「比心」。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mk54rtil1jus\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">在不同的展馆，不同的厂商在用机器人展示叠衣服的场景，甚至三星这样的消费巨头也在其中，同样每次展示时都会有相当多观众围观。但每次看到这样的场景时，都不禁会让人怀疑，叠衣服到底是不是最适合机器人的场景——我们知道大概率多年后人类不用再叠衣服，但至少现在，让机器人帮人类代劳，投入产出比可能不太高。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mk54rtil10oa\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">就像当年智能驾驶和新能源车的技术成熟、并且供应链开始「溢出」。机器人本体虽然尚未形成一个能商业闭环的产业，但疯狂内卷的中国机器人供应链，也提前数年开始「溢出」。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mk54rtil7fw\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">例如，本次展览中最让笔者惊艳的产品——智能轮椅，让人惊叹国内企业能将如此细分的赛道的天花板，卷到如此之高。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mk54rtil1587\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">在小神童 XSTO 展台，笔者看到智能轮椅产品不仅配备了「麦克纳姆轮」这样的前轮，而且能丝滑的前进后退和原地掉头，并且能通过相当大坡度的坡道，进阶产品甚至能上楼梯。这样看似科幻的产品，让即便身体健全的人都想试一试。鉴于当代年轻人，都已经以电动轮椅取代共享单车进行代步，智能轮椅成为一个新的风口，并不让人特别奇怪。</span></p>\n  <p class=\"channels_iframe_wrp\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <div></div>\n  <p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mk54rtil1d48\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">曾经在极客公园创新大会 2026 上进行演讲的 HyperShell 极壳科技，在 CES 上特地搭了几层的楼梯，吸引观众们穿上外骨骼产品现场爬楼，体验机器带你「健步如飞」的感觉。看到观众们穿着外骨骼产品，在三段楼梯上鱼贯上下的画面，不得不说比较超现实。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mk54rtil1olk\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">在碳基人类和硅基 AI 结合之前，可能还是先经过和坚硬金属结合的初级阶段。</span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"title\">\n   <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mk54owl1k5p\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n     <div style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:16px;margin-right:8px;text-align:justify;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n      <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n       <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;min-width: 10%;height: auto;flex: 0 0 auto;align-self: flex-start;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n        <div style=\"isolation: isolate;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n         <div style=\"font-size: 36px;line-height: 1;letter-spacing: 0px;color: rgb(45, 113, 214);\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n          <p style=\"clear: both;min-height: 1em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk54rtili72\"><em><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\">03</span></strong></em></span></p>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <p mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:17px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" mpa-font-style=\"mk54rtil100a\"><span style=\"\" mpa-is-content=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-mpa-template&quot;:&quot;t&quot;,&quot;mpa-paragraph-type&quot;:&quot;title&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;mpa-from-tpl&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;strong&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.578px; text-align: center;&quot;,&quot;mpa-from-tpl&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;mpa-is-content&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">黄色的「彩蛋」</span></span></strong></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mk54rtil1x7g\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">CES 开展第一天，在展馆还没开放的时候，今年 CES 最大的赢家，已经出现了——影石 Insta360。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"image\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-w=\"4096\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"434\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=fc361d64&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F8cu01Kavc5baH4tGiaub6Npb9iaA2ArVhicAjvrb1NgYZHSpsetZKe0GycOBNJ3sqDb7CwGiaaVpVic1pkBLuF4wLnQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"secondTitle\">\n   <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1em;text-align:justify;margin-right:8px;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\" data-pm-slice=\"3 2 []\"><strong style=\"text-align: left;color: rgb(255, 47, 0);font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" mpa-font-style=\"mk54rtil1lp5\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-weight: normal;\">Insta360 的黄色袋子成了 CES 的标配｜图片来源：极客公园</span></span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mk54rtilspb\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">展馆内、展馆外，排队的人，人人肩上、手中都随身携带着一个明黄色的便携袋子，后者在每个展馆门前供所有参会者免费领取。而这样一个抢占人们心智的绝佳机会，现在被影石捷足先登。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mk54rtilmtl\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">此前多年，这种黄色的「CES 非官方制服」，赞助商都是老牌影像企业尼康，而随着昔日老大的业务调整以及 CES 对这个「黄金展位」的策略调整，让影石代替尼康，成为人们身边的一道亮黄。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mk54rtilna2\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">从某种意义上来看，黄色手袋的易主，正代表了影石及其新生代影像公司所代表的「计算光学」，取代尼康这样昔日的「光学计算」巨头的结果。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mk54rtilohv\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">拉斯维加斯 LED 光源几英里外的地方就是沙漠，你很难想象这片沙漠之地的名字的本意是「有泉水的地方」。在多入沙粒的「饺子机」的叮叮作响中，维加斯会展中心的科技创业者心中的 idea，则像泉水一样，暗自滋养着科技行业未来的绿洲。</span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文深入报道了 2026 年 CES 展会，揭示了 AI 如何深度融入汽车、机器人及消费电子产品，并特别指出中国车企在智能化方面的领先，以及影石 Insta360 通过市场策略成为展会“最大赢家”。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文深入报道了 2026 年 CES 展会，揭示了 AI 如何深度融入汽车、机器人及消费电子产品，并特别指出中国车企在智能化方面的领先，以及影石 Insta360 通过市场策略成为展会“最大赢家”。",
  "summary": "2026 年 CES 展会再次聚焦人工智能，展示了 AI 技术从概念走向深度融合的趋势。文章指出，AI 已不再是独立强调的卖点，而是广泛渗透到智能汽车、机器人、智能家居等各类消费电子产品中。中国汽车制造商吉利和长城凭借先进的全域 AI 战略和高阶智驾技术，在展会上展现出超越国际同行的智能化水平。此外，具身智能和机器人（特别是灵巧手、智能轮椅和外骨骼）成为展会热点，中国供应链在此领域展现出强大的“溢出效应”。文章还意外披露了影石 Insta360 通过赞助 CES 官方便携袋、取代尼康，成功抢占了参会者的心智，成为本届 CES 的最大“赢家”，象征着“计算光学”对传统“光学计算”的超越。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "AI 已深度融入各种消费电子产品和场景，成为默认选项而非独立卖点。",
      "explanation": "文章通过冰箱、电视、汽车、智能眼镜等例子，说明 AI 已从展板上的概念融化到具体产品中，强调了 AI 的普遍性和无处不在。"
    },
